; LOGBOOK OF UPDATES IN THIS FILE
; –Date— |––Description———————————–
; 20260427  v2.0  Created the proactive main bot agentA and added setup logic with FSM start state BotCreatePost. (Ali)
; 20260429  v2.1  Added post creation logic with topic, extremity, post-id, labels and placement in the feed-zone. (Abdulmajid)
; 20260502  v2.2  Implemented the proactive FSM states BotCreatePost and EvaluateBotPost for creating, broadcasting and evaluating active posts. (Abdulmajid och Ali)
; 20260502  v2.3  Added reactive command flags createPostFlag, broadcastPostFlag and generateSimilarPostFlag to connect the proactive and reactive layers. (Abdulmajid och Ali)
; 20260506  v2.4  Added broadcasting from agentA to agentBs using inform messages when a new post is created. (Abdulmajid)
; 20260506  v2.5  Added post status monitoring with viral detection based on shares and likes, including movement to viral-zone. (Ali)
; 20260509  v2.6  Added logic for generating similar posts from viral or removed posts using parent-post-id and mutated extremity. (Abdulmajid och Ali)
; 20260509  v2.7  Added post label updates showing post-id, shares, likes, viral status and removed status. (Ali)
; 20260511  v2.8  Added social communication with humans using request messages for promoting extreme posts. (Abdulmajid)
; 20260510  v2.9  Added handling of agree/refuse replies from humans and counters for accepted and rejected promote requests. (Abdulmajid)
; 20260518  v3.0  Added contract-net style request logic where agentA sends viral-contract requests to reactive bots. (Abdulmajid)
; 20260520  v3.1  Added contract response tracking with contractAgreeCount, contractRefuseCount and contractRequestSent?. (Ali)
; 20260522  v3.2  Improved updateEnvironmentInfo_agentAs so agentA observes active posts, viral posts and removed posts every tick. (Abdulmajid och Ali)
; 20260527  v3.3  Added protection against removed active posts getting stuck before broadcast by redirecting them to BotGenerateSimilarPost. (Abdulmajid)
; 20260528  v3.4  Improved fallback logic in do-generate-similar-post so a normal post is created if no previous post exists. (Ali)
; 20260528  v3.5  Refined the hybrid architecture separation so the proactive FSM selects actions and the reactive layer executes one concrete action per tick. (Ali)
